data.description: Great home in the incredibly desirable neighborhood of McFarland Farms. As you walk in the front door you will be welcomed by a tile entryway and will see the beautiful staircase, which leads to the spacious upstairs bedrooms. The kitchen and living room have an open floor plan and have a great view of the fenced in backyard. Enjoy entertaining family and friends in the backyard while splashing around in your in-ground swimming pool. (2023) New Roof. (2013) crawlspace was waterproofed and new kitchen appliances were purchased. (2014) furnace, water heater, and AC system replaced. (2015) new pool heater system installed. Pool cleaning robot conveys. A great home, in a great neighborhood, at a great price! Home is being sold with a Home Warranty. New gutters will be completed when new buyer selects color. Motivated Seller!!!
